| Problem             | Stack Maintains        | Stack Order  | Traverse | Stores      |
| ------------------- | ---------------------- | ------------ | -------- | ----------- |
| Daily Temperatures  | Next greater temp      | Decreasing   | R â†’ L    | Indices     |
| Histogram Max Area  | Next smaller heights   | Increasing   | L â†’ R    | Indices     |
| Trapping Rain Water | Lower walls            | Decreasing   | L â†’ R    | Indices     |
| Stock Span          | Previous greater price | Decreasing   | L â†’ R    | Indices     |
| Remove K Digits     | Smallest number        | Increasing   | L â†’ R    | Digits      |
| Asteroid Collision  | Collision candidates   | Custom order | L â†’ R    | Sizes/signs |

